        "created_at": "2025-12-11T22:06:58.845Z",
        "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/4/2/429899fa35e76172156ba872adcdb66a88ba451e.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/429899fa35e76172156ba872adcdb66a88ba451e\" title=\"IMG_7520\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/4/2/429899fa35e76172156ba872adcdb66a88ba451e_2_690x229.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_7520\" data-base62-sha1=\"9v8sx0Adl6abd6qP1dR9cRpxUV8\" width=\"690\" height=\"229\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/4/2/429899fa35e76172156ba872adcdb66a88ba451e_2_690x229.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/4/2/429899fa35e76172156ba872adcdb66a88ba451e_2_1035x343.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/4/2/429899fa35e76172156ba872adcdb66a88ba451e.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"1F181E\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_7520</span><span class=\"informations\">1151×383 32.5 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>You get the above three options when you swipe a chat in iOS on mobile</p>\n<p>One architecture option (noting it is based on a right-hander’s use of the mobile interface) to lessen the likelihood would be to move ‘delete’ to the far left, have ‘archive’ in the middle, and have ‘mute’ on the far right - ie., least destructive action to most destructive action.</p>",
